```plantuml
@startuml UBC-CIC_Student-Connect-App

actor User
participant "React Frontend" as Frontend
participant "AWS Cognito" as Cognito
participant "GraphQL API" as GraphQL
participant "Lambda Functions" as Lambda
participant "DynamoDB" as DynamoDB
participant "Elasticsearch" as ES
participant "External Sources" as Sources

User -> Frontend: Access Application
Frontend -> Cognito: Authenticate User
Cognito --> Frontend: Authentication Token

User -> Frontend: Complete Survey
Frontend -> GraphQL: Submit Preferences
GraphQL -> DynamoDB: Store User Preferences

loop Data Aggregation
    Lambda -> Sources: Fetch Data (Events/News/Blogs)
    Sources --> Lambda: Raw Data
    Lambda -> DynamoDB: Store Processed Data
    DynamoDB -> Lambda: Trigger Stream
    Lambda -> ES: Sync Data
end

User -> Frontend: Request Personalized Content
Frontend -> GraphQL: Query Content
GraphQL -> ES: Search by Preferences
ES --> GraphQL: Filtered Results
GraphQL --> Frontend: Display Content

User -> Frontend: Save Content
Frontend -> GraphQL: Update Saved Items
GraphQL -> DynamoDB: Store User Saved Items

@enduml
```